'''[[Tech specialist]] belts''' were [[Utility belt/Legends|utility belts]] worn by those specializing in technical fields in the period surrounding the [[Mandalorian Wars]] and the [[Jedi Civil War]]. They contained tools useful in creating potent upgrades, as well as defeating computer security systems.

